description.en: Sancoj Opportunity Supermarket. It is a marketplace to buy and sell goods & services, find jobs, freelance projects, scholarships, government empowerment, distributorship and franchise deals, events, bounty, airdrops and more, while socializing with people of same interest for free. It also uses AI to predict and suggest the most profitable opportunities for users.
